<% content_for :title, "Privacy Policy" %>

<section class="pt-28 pb-16 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 space-y-10">
    <header class="space-y-3">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Last updated: <%= Time.zone.today.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></p>
    </header>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
      <section class="space-y-2">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Overview</h2>
        <p>This policy explains how we collect, use, and share information when you use this site.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-2">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>When you sign in with Google, we receive basic profile data such as your name, email address, and profile image.</p>
        <p>We also collect information you provide directly, such as contact form submissions.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-2">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">How We Use Information</h2>
        <p>We use your information to authenticate your account, respond to requests, and improve the site.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-2">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Sharing</h2>
        <p>We do not sell your personal information. We only share data with service providers required to operate the site.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-2">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Data Retention</h2>
        <p>We retain account information for as long as your account is active or as needed to provide the service.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-2">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Contact</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this policy, please use the contact form on the site.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
